snippet.title: Amber Heard looks stunning in chic ruffled two-piece in Italy
snippet.description:
She is currently in Italy attending the Giffoni Film Festival.
And Amber Heard put on a stunning display as she was honoured with a Giffoni Experience Award in Giffoni Valle Piana on Thursday evening, following her service to film and charity.
The Aquaman actress, 33, opted for a pretty feminine two-piece, including a stylish cowl neck strapless top and a frilly wrap skirt in the same pattern.
